node.text:
@buffalobills OL Dion Dawkins (@jerzeystar) shares why it is vital we address our criminal justice system and the importance of second chances. The NFL’s @inspirechange initiative helps organizations like @alabamaappleseed provide those second chances.
 
To learn more about the NFL's efforts to address barriers to opportunity and equality, visit NFL.com/InspireChange. #InspireChange

node.title: Four Pillars of Inspire Change – Criminal Justice Reform

node.text:
@rams OL @andrewwhitworth77 is a believer in the power of education and providing opportunity to communities that have traditionally been left behind. Through his work and organizations like @dream.corps, we can work together toward education equality.
 
To learn more about the NFL's efforts to address barriers to opportunity and equality, visit NFL.com/InspireChange. #InspireChange

node.title: Four Pillars of Inspire Change – Education

node.text: NFL legend Michael Robinson shares his personal story, the importance of having a support system and how @seahawks  Head Coach Pete Carroll helped Michael nurture his own mental health. For more information, or to seek help, visit www.mhanational.org.

node.title: NFL Mental Health & Wellness Series | Michael Robinson
